metadata.name: Zion: The Above
metadata.description:
Above The Zion. A look into a futuristic version of The City of Toronto.

About the editing

My passion for futurism is incorporated into each piece by using color-grading techniques. The goal was to create a feel of a futuristic city out of Toronto downtown. 

Location: Financial District, Toronto, Canada

Artwork: 1/1

Artist: Izekh Angeles

Asset: 5472 × 3078

Date: April 2022
